{
    "story_id": "",
    "story_name": "失落的龙约 第26章 5-2 “心”",
    "story_icon": "",
    "outline": {
        "title": [
            "剧情概要"
        ],
        "content": [
            "莫尔提斯为了保护伊莉雅而受了致命伤。\\n意识到自己命不久矣的莫尔提斯\\n将创世之器的重任托付给了王子。\\n分散各处的伙伴们也终于赶来，\\n王子与泽诺斯展开了最终的决战！"
        ]
    },
    "story_content": [
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110367_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "伊莉雅",
            "context": "啊！？糟糕……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_26_11_0001",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110369_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莫尔提斯",
            "context": "伊莉雅啊啊啊啊啊！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_26_11_0002",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110367_01",
                "110369_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "伊莉雅",
            "context": "诶？莫、莫尔提斯！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_26_11_0003",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110369_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莫尔提斯",
            "context": "你、你没事……吧？伊莉雅……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_26_11_0004",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110369_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "伊莉雅",
            "context": "为什么……\\n为什么要替我挡下来！？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_26_11_0005",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110369_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莫尔提斯",
            "context": "没有……为什么……\\n救自己喜欢的人不需要理由……\\n这还是你教我的……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_26_11_0006",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110369_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "伊莉雅",
            "context": "你、你这傻瓜……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_26_11_0007",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100053_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "泽诺斯",
            "context": "明白了吧？\\n所以我才决定舍弃自己的心。\\n信赖只不过是束缚自己的枷锁。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_26_11_0008",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110367_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "伊莉雅",
            "context": "泽诺斯……\\n你竟敢……竟敢将莫尔提斯……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_26_11_0009",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100009_08"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "泽娜",
            "context": "冷静一点！伊莉雅！\\n要是我们现在再失去你的话，\\n莫尔提斯的牺牲就白费了！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_26_11_0010",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110367_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "伊莉雅",
            "context": "唔……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_26_11_0011",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100053_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "泽诺斯",
            "context": "因愤怒而失去理智……\\n这都是心所导致的。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_26_11_0012",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100053_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "泽诺斯",
            "context": "乖乖地臣服于我把。\\n完美的世界之中没有愤怒，\\n我会消除世间一切悲伤与痛苦。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_26_11_0013",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110367_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "伊莉雅",
            "context": "我们的人生还没有无聊到\\n会让我们向往那种莫名其妙的世界！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_26_11_0014",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100053_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "泽诺斯",
            "context": "是吗。\\n不过无聊确实会给人\\n带来难以忍受的痛苦。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_26_11_0015",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100053_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "泽诺斯",
            "context": "回想起来，\\n我之所以创造世界，\\n也正是因为没能忍受无聊的生活。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_26_11_0016",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100053_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "泽诺斯",
            "context": "也许至今为止我所做的一切\\n都是为了打发那无聊的时间吧。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_26_11_0017",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100044_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "席菈",
            "context": "什么……\\n你想说我们只不过是\\n你打发时间的工具吗！？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_26_11_0018",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100053_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "泽诺斯",
            "context": "这么想的话，\\n你们倒也不算是一无是处。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_26_11_0019",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100053_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "泽诺斯",
            "context": "你们能让我负伤虽然令我吃惊，\\n但同时也令我兴奋。\\n来吧……接下来你们要如何取悦我？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_26_11_0020",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100043_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "奥莉加",
            "context": "可恶，你这目中无人的家伙！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_26_11_0021",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100039_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "奈迪犹",
            "context": "好吧，泽诺斯！\\n接下来由我来当你的对手！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_26_11_0022",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_14"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "奈迪犹！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_26_11_0023",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210162_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "奈迪犹",
            "context": "赶快去治疗莫尔提斯！\\n如果失去了他，我们就没有胜算了！\\n我来争取时间！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_26_11_0024",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100053_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "泽诺斯",
            "context": "巴哈姆特吗……\\n但我丝毫感受不到如往日那般的力量。\\n无聊至极……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_26_11_0025",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210162_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "奈迪犹",
            "context": "唔……快点！\\n我坚持不了多久……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_26_11_0026",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100054_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "塞西娅",
            "context": "好的！\\n莫尔提斯，坚持住！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_26_11_0027",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110369_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莫尔提斯",
            "context": "抱歉……我已经不行了。\\n我自己最清楚……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_26_11_0028",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110367_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "伊莉雅",
            "context": "傻瓜！我可从来没有教过你\\n可以轻易放弃性命！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_26_11_0029",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110369_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莫尔提斯",
            "context": "对不起，伊莉雅……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_26_11_0030",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110369_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莫尔提斯",
            "context": "在我死之前……\\n有一件事无论如何都要说出来……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_26_11_0031",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110369_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莫尔提斯",
            "context": "能代替……我的人……\\n就是你，尤蒂尔。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_26_11_0032",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_14"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "诶！？代替你！？\\n这是什么意思，莫尔提斯！？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_26_11_0033",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110369_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莫尔提斯",
            "context": "你来代替我……\\n成为创世之力的容器，\\n与泽诺斯抗衡……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_26_11_0034",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_14"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "创世之力的容器！？\\n我真的能做到吗！？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_26_11_0035",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110369_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莫尔提斯",
            "context": "我一直……都很好奇。\\n尤蒂尔的心到底从何而来。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_26_11_0036",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_14"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "我的心？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_26_11_0037",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100044_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "席菈",
            "context": "我明白你的意思……\\n尤蒂尔的身体和我一样，\\n都是由魔神的肉体制造出来的。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_26_11_0038",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100044_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "席菈",
            "context": "可他的心却和我不同，\\n他的心并不是来自自身。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_26_11_0039",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100044_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "席菈",
            "context": "他是用精灵秘术制造出来，\\n用来复活本应已死的第七王子的。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_26_11_0040",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100044_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "席菈",
            "context": "所以尤蒂尔的心\\n本应和我一样，承载着原本的心，\\n也就是第七王子的心……可是——",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_26_11_0041",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100044_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "席菈",
            "context": "真正的第七王子却是奈迪犹……\\n所以尤蒂尔的魔神肉体里\\n跳动的不可能是第七王子的心……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_26_11_0042",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100044_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "席菈",
            "context": "而且我的心因魔神的肉体而坏掉，\\n可尤蒂尔却……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_26_11_0043",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110369_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莫尔提斯",
            "context": "没错……魔神肉体由黑暗魔力形成……\\n这世上能够不受其侵蚀的心\\n只有一个……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_26_11_0044",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100054_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "塞西娅",
            "context": "等、等一下……\\n那哥哥的心岂不是——",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_26_11_0045",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110369_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莫尔提斯",
            "context": "和我一样……是泽诺斯的“心”。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_26_11_0046",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110367_01",
                "100054_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "全员",
            "context": "！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_26_11_0047",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_14"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "我竟然是……泽诺斯的“心”……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_26_11_0048",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110369_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莫尔提斯",
            "context": "我也是在这要塞种才得以确信。\\n尤蒂尔对泽诺斯\\n所在的方向掌握得非常精准。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_26_11_0049",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110369_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莫尔提斯",
            "context": "他应该是在潜意识中\\n与泽诺斯相互吸引……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_26_11_0050",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_14"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "相互吸引……\\n我的确感受到了泽诺斯所在的方向……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_26_11_0051",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_14"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "我会有那种感觉，\\n是因为我也是泽诺斯的一部分吗……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_26_11_0052",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110369_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莫尔提斯",
            "context": "我是泽诺斯的“接受他人之心”。\\n而你则是“为他人奉献之心”……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_26_11_0053",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110369_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莫尔提斯",
            "context": "为他人着想\\n并祈祷他人幸福的心……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_26_11_0054",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110369_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莫尔提斯",
            "context": "所以，接下来就交给你了，\\n尤蒂尔……\\n我已经……帮不了什么了……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_26_11_0055",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110367_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "伊莉雅",
            "context": "莫尔提斯！不要啊！\\n我不许你死！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_26_11_0056",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110369_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莫尔提斯",
            "context": "伊莉雅……对不起……\\n谢谢你，能像这样死去，我很开心……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_26_11_0057",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110367_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "伊莉雅",
            "context": "你在说些什么……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_26_11_0058",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110369_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莫尔提斯",
            "context": "我本一无所有。\\n无论是自己的意志，还是所珍视之人，\\n我一切都不曾拥有。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_26_11_0059",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110369_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莫尔提斯",
            "context": "直到我遇见了你。你教会了我\\n什么是爱，让我有了想要守护的人，\\n也让我拥有了遵从本心的意志。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_26_11_0060",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110369_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莫尔提斯",
            "context": "所以……原本一无所有的我能够\\n以自己的意志为保护心爱之人而死……\\n没有什么比这更能令我高兴的了……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_26_11_0061",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110369_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莫尔提斯",
            "context": "谢谢……你……伊莉……雅……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_26_11_0062",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110367_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "伊莉雅",
            "context": "莫尔提斯！\\n莫尔提斯啊啊啊啊！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_26_11_0063",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110367_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "伊莉雅",
            "context": "……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_26_11_0064",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_14"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "伊莉雅……\\n我知道这对你很不公平，可是……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_26_11_0065",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110367_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "伊莉雅",
            "context": "我明白……若是我在这里一蹶不振，\\n莫尔提斯的努力就白费了。\\n我决不会允许这种事情发生。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_26_11_0066",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110367_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "伊莉雅",
            "context": "各位，我们开始吧。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_26_11_0067",
